35
00:04:06,870 --> 00:04:08,470
and his pride.

36
00:04:09,670 --> 00:04:11,870
You and your mother are nothing but bad luck.

37
00:04:12,300 --> 00:04:13,800
If you stay in my life,

38
00:04:14,300 --> 00:04:15,670
