39
00:04:16,130 --> 00:04:18,000
If I didn’t need your help,

40
00:04:18,329 --> 00:04:19,600
I would’ve forgotten about you already.

41
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:30,450
But I made a promise to myself—

42
00:04:30,450 --> 00:04:33,100
I won’t let anyone hurt me again.

43
00:04:35,530 --> 00:04:36,330
Po.

44
00:04:39,370 --> 00:04:42,270
No matter what I face tomorrow,

45
00:04:42,640 --> 00:04:46,310
I’m ready to face it.

46
00:05:26,370 --> 00:05:28,960
I used to hate my father so much.

47
00:05:29,190 --> 00:05:30,510
But now,

48
00:05:31,170 --> 00:05:33,870
I can finally let everything go.

49
00:05:40,670 --> 00:05:42,770
Sasom never left.

50
00:05:43,190 --> 00:05:45,990
Every time I wake up startled,

51
00:05:46,840 --> 00:05:48,360
