52
00:05:49,670 --> 00:05:51,590
so I know he’s there.

53
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:54,190
And now,

54
00:05:54,610 --> 00:05:57,210
I’ve become addicted to sleeping in his arms.

55
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:34,250
From now on,

56
00:06:36,830 --> 00:06:38,870
I won’t have anything weighing on me anymore.

57
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:42,060
I can start over

58
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:44,270
with the one I love.

59
00:07:08,300 --> 00:07:09,100
Babe.

60
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:11,500
Babe, come here.

61
00:07:13,500 --> 00:07:14,330
Babe.

62
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:18,600
Yes?

63
00:07:23,330 --> 00:07:25,070
You’re really cute.

64
00:07:26,730 --> 00:07:27,570
