75
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:09,130
I want to decorate the room,

76
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:11,400
and get a tall Christmas tree.

77
00:08:12,100 --> 00:08:15,500
And I was thinking of inviting our close friends

78
00:08:15,670 --> 00:08:17,000
