79
00:08:17,900 --> 00:08:18,700
Hmm.

80
00:08:20,570 --> 00:08:22,470
You don’t have to go yourself.

81
00:08:23,470 --> 00:08:24,370
It’s no big deal.

82
00:08:24,870 --> 00:08:26,170
I’ll have Inn handle it.

83
00:08:26,470 --> 00:08:28,370
How tall do you want it?

84
00:08:28,670 --> 00:08:29,930
Just tell me.

85
00:08:33,270 --> 00:08:34,130
As for money,

86
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:36,270
I’ll give you as much as you want.

87
00:08:42,730 --> 00:08:45,250
I thought you’d spoil me.

88
00:08:48,340 --> 00:08:49,310
I will.

89
00:08:49,730 --> 00:08:50,970
Let me have my way.

90
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:52,940
