91
00:08:53,670 --> 00:08:55,010
But—

92
00:08:55,250 --> 00:08:57,130
If you’re spoiling me, there can’t be a “but.”

93
00:08:57,690 --> 00:08:59,290
Then you have to take me now.

94
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,950
Right now.

95
00:09:05,700 --> 00:09:06,520
But…

96
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:07,670
Otherwise,

97
00:09:09,170 --> 00:09:10,770
