100
00:09:18,930 --> 00:09:19,730
Right now?

101
00:09:30,130 --> 00:09:30,930
Right now.

102
00:09:51,400 --> 00:09:52,400
Just like I said,

103
00:09:54,300 --> 00:09:56,600
Sasom has spoiled me rotten.

104
00:09:57,870 --> 00:09:59,370
From someone who used to wake up early,

105
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:02,070
