106
00:10:03,370 --> 00:10:04,870
From someone who used to work hard,

107
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:08,300
now I just lie around watching series.

108
00:10:09,570 --> 00:10:11,200
From someone who used to take care of him,

109
00:10:13,130 --> 00:10:16,400
