123
00:12:47,100 --> 00:12:47,900
Khun.

124
00:12:48,400 --> 00:12:49,770
Because you’re cute.

125
00:12:53,070 --> 00:12:54,330
Or don’t you like it?

126
00:12:58,930 --> 00:12:59,730
I like it.

127
00:14:13,900 --> 00:14:16,970
Khun, this gold one is really beautiful.

128
00:14:25,130 --> 00:14:26,800
Everyone confirmed they’re coming.

129
00:14:27,730 --> 00:14:30,870
Sasom never hosts parties like this.

130
00:14:31,800 --> 00:14:34,870
This is the first year he said he wants to spend time with friends,

131
00:14:35,730 --> 00:14:36,530
