132
00:14:37,100 --> 00:14:38,200
and the people he loves.

133
00:14:42,500 --> 00:14:43,550
And then?

134
00:14:44,580 --> 00:14:46,320
The person he loves…

135
00:14:47,590 --> 00:14:49,190
