136
00:16:04,170 --> 00:16:05,000
What’s with you?

137
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:06,400
Give me a massage.

138
00:16:52,370 --> 00:16:53,500
What do you want?

139
00:16:56,730 --> 00:16:58,770
I want to eat your cooking.

140
00:17:08,730 --> 00:17:11,099
I haven’t had a meal with you in a long time.

141
00:17:11,500 --> 00:17:12,300
I miss it.

142
00:17:15,500 --> 00:17:16,300
Then—

143
00:17:18,730 --> 00:17:20,170
let me cook for you.

144
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:22,800
Please.

145
00:17:23,500 --> 00:17:24,300
Please.

146
00:17:30,200 --> 00:17:31,100
You’re not allowed.

147
00:17:42,500 --> 00:17:43,480
