151
00:18:54,730 --> 00:18:55,600
Hello everyone.

152
00:18:57,300 --> 00:18:58,500
It’s been a while.

153
00:19:00,970 --> 00:19:02,570
I hope everyone is doing well.

154
00:19:05,800 --> 00:19:07,810
First of all,

155
00:19:07,810 --> 00:19:10,130
I want to thank everyone

156
00:19:10,560 --> 00:19:12,030
