157
00:19:12,260 --> 00:19:15,320
for applying to become my new peaches.

158
00:19:35,370 --> 00:19:37,160
I’m really happy

159
00:19:38,000 --> 00:19:39,640
to know that

160
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:41,680
so many people

161
00:19:41,680 --> 00:19:44,350
want me to taste them.

162
00:19:58,200 --> 00:20:00,670
But I have to be honest with you all—

163
00:20:02,270 --> 00:20:04,170
I can’t go on anymore.

164
00:20:11,270 --> 00:20:12,180
Because I

165
00:20:13,350 --> 00:20:14,930
just met someone.

166
00:20:23,500 --> 00:20:24,300
Yes.

167
00:20:27,300 --> 00:20:28,670
I’m in love.

168
00:20:43,370 --> 00:20:45,470
In a way I’ve never felt before.

169
00:20:49,270 --> 00:20:51,100
He’s taught me so many things.

170
00:21:00,100 --> 00:21:01,300
I won’t regret it.

171
00:21:02,470 --> 00:21:03,570
We won’t regret it.

172
00:21:07,130 --> 00:21:08,510
Most importantly,

173
00:21:09,030 --> 00:21:12,250
he taught me how to protect

174
00:21:12,670 --> 00:21:16,640
the one I love—keep him happy and safe.

175
00:21:18,600 --> 00:21:19,930
Don’t let go of my hand.

176
00:21:22,300 --> 00:21:23,470
I promise.

177
00:21:27,730 --> 00:21:28,530
Therefore,

178
00:21:36,700 --> 00:21:38,520
I would like to announce

179
00:21:38,890 --> 00:21:41,440
the Peach Lover account will be closed,

180
00:21:42,190 --> 00:21:44,100
starting from this moment on.

181
00:21:46,350 --> 00:21:47,820
Thank you, everyone.

182
00:21:48,720 --> 00:21:50,920
for supporting me all this time.

183
00:22:02,000 --> 00:22:03,560
And lastly,

184
00:22:04,130 --> 00:22:07,100
Merry Christmas and Happy New Year.

185
00:22:08,550 --> 00:22:10,000
Goodbye, everyone.

186
00:23:00,600 --> 00:23:01,770
Can I ask you something?

187
00:23:03,300 --> 00:23:04,100
Sure.

188
00:23:06,330 --> 00:23:07,730
What flower do you like the most?

189
00:23:09,930 --> 00:23:10,730
You mean—

190
00:23:12,670 --> 00:23:13,470
